iption','<p>PBMA’s H. V. Desai Eye Hospital has all the latest equipment, which includes an ND:YAG laser machine, B Scan facility, Pentacam, Phaco machine, portable vitrectomy facility, Lumenis multisport laser machine, and a Mobile Eye Care van facility, to provide the highest quality of services to patients. In addition, it has a team of highly experienced specialists with years of experience. What’s more, the hospital’s skills & training centre ensures that its in-house doctors are updated with all the latest techniques and knowledge related to their field. \r\n</p><div class=\"learn-more-wrapper\"><button class=\"learn-more\">Learn More</button></div>'),(2307,387,'_state_of_art_description','field_5cc1803f1ddc3'),(2308,387,'pioneer_img_1','159'),(2309,387,'_pioneer_img_1','field_5ccc399e2f48c'),(2310,387,'pioneer_name_1','Late Mr. Tukaram Bamankar'),(2311,387,'_pioneer_name_1','field_5ccc3a062f48d'),(2312,387,'pioneer_link_1','a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:5:\"Learn\";s:3:\"url\";s:1:\"#\";s:6:\"target\";s:0:\"\";}'),(2313,387,'_pioneer_link_1','field_5ccc3a172f48e'),(2314,387,'pioneer_img_2','79'),(2315,387,'_pioneer_img_2','field_5ccc3abea352f'),(2316,387,'pioneer_name_2','Late Mr. Niranjan Pandya'),(2317,387,'_pioneer_name_2','field_5ccc3ae3a3530'),(2318,387,'pioneer_link_2','a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:5:\"Learn\";s:3:\"url\";s:1:\"#\";s:6:\"target\";s:0:\"\";}'),(2319,387,'_pioneer_link_2','field_5ccc3afca3531'),(2320,387,'awards','<div class=\"award-content\">Prestigious awards & recognition received <br> by the hospital and its team of doctors</div><div class=\"award-images\"><div class=\"award-1\"><div class=\"award-img\"><img src=\"wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/NABH.jpg\" alt=\"image-award\" /></div><div class=\"award-name\"><span><strong>NABH</strong></span> <span>Accredited Hospital</span></div></div><div class=\"award-1\"><div class=\"award-img\"><img src=\"wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/Padma-Shri-Medallion.jpg\" alt=\"image-award\" /></div><div class=\"award-name\"><span>Late Mr. Niranjan Pandya was honoured by theGovernment of India, with the fourth highestIndian civilian award of </span><span><strong>Padma Shri.</strong></span></div></div><div class=\"award-1\"><div class=\"award-img\"><img src=\"wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/APAO.jpg\" alt=\"image-award\" /></div><div class=\"award-name\"><span>Dr. Col.(Retd) Madan Deshpande, has been awarded ‘Outstanding Service in Prevention of Blindness Award by </span><span><strong> ‘Asia Pacific Academy</strong></span><span> <strong>of Ophthalmology (APAO)’ </strong></span></div></div></div>'),(2321,387,'_awards','field_5ccf2762d6c5a'),(2322,387,'creating_ophthalmologists_image','173'),(2323,387,'_creating_ophthalmologists_image','field_5ccf29afa38af'),(2324,387,'creating_ophthalmologists_description','<div class=\"ophthalmologists-title clear-both\"><span>Training Programs & Skill Transfer</span></div><div class=\"ophthalmologists-content clear-both\"><p>In addition to eye care, the hospital also conducts short-term and long-term fellowship programs that help practicing ophthalmologists upgrade their skills. Under the skill transfer program, the hospital has trained over 600 ophthalmologists nominated by the Government of India, as well as private ophthalmologists from India and abroad. </p><p><button class=\"learn-more\">Apply Now</button></p></div>'),(2325,387,'_creating_ophthalmologists_description','field_5ccf29f5a38b0'),(2326,387,'success_story','<div class=\"success-content\">A quick glance at few opportunities received by the hospital <br />  to restore the vision of the needy.</div><div class=\"success-story clear-both\"><div class=\"success-1\"><div class=\"success-name\">Vasant Balid</div><div class=\"success-desig\">Farmer, Junnar Maharashtra</div><div class=\"success-desc\"><p>Vasant underwent screening at a camp conducted by H.V. Desai Eye Hospital in his district, with the support of Wonderworks & Vision.</p><p>At the camp, he was diagnosed to have cat