uloplasty-2','','','2019-05-09 06:34:32','2019-05-09 06:34:32','',71,'http://local.hvd.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Oculoplasty.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(165,1,'2019-05-09 06:34:33','2019-05-09 06:34:33','','Ped. Opthalomolgy','','inherit','open','closed','','ped-opthalomolgy-2','','','2019-05-09 06:34:33','2019-05-09 06:34:33','',71,'http://local.hvd.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Ped.-Opthalomolgy.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(166,1,'2019-05-09 06:34:33','2019-05-09 06:34:33','','Retina','','inherit','open','closed','','retina-2','','','2019-05-09 06:34:33','2019-05-09 06:34:33','',71,'http://local.hvd.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Retina.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(167,1,'2019-05-09 06:34:33','2019-05-09 06:34:33','','Uveitis','','inherit','open','closed','','uveitis-2','','','2019-05-09 06:34:33','2019-05-09 06:34:33','',71,'http://local.hvd.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Uveitis.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(168,1,'2019-05-09 06:34:33','2019-05-09 06:34:33','','Cataract','','inherit','open','closed','','cataract-2','','','2019-05-09 06:34:33','2019-05-09 06:34:33','',71,'http://local.hvd.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Cataract.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(169,1,'2019-05-09 06:34:34','2019-05-09 06:34:34','','Contact-Lens','','inherit','open','closed','','contact-lens-2','','','2019-05-09 06:34:34','2019-05-09 06:34:34','',71,'http://local.hvd.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Contact-Lens.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(170,1,'2019-05-09 06:34:34','2019-05-09 06:34:34','','Cornea','','inherit','open','closed','','cornea-2','','','2019-05-09 06:34:34','2019-05-09 06:34:34','',71,'http://local.hvd.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Cornea.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(172,1,'2019-06-11 12:13:28','2019-06-11 12:13:28','<div class=\"breadcrumbs mb-4 clear-both\"><a href=\"/\">Home</a> / Our Facilities / Specialities /<strong> Ped. Opthalomolgy </strong></div>\n\nPaediatric Ophthalmology and Squint Department:\n\nVision impairment in childhood has a dramatic impact not only on the social development of a child, but also on his/her learning ability and potential. As certain serious eye disorders produce no early warning symptoms, it becomes all the more necessary to know when to get your child evaluated by a qualified professional.\n\nThe paediatric ophthalmology services offered at H. V. Desai Eye Hospital are dedicated to provide comprehensive ophthalmic care to children aged below 16 years. The provision of these services is aimed at ensuring that no child is becomes blind, and to provide equal rights to children suffering from low vision as well as increased accessibility to all the possible medical services to enable them to play an active role in society. The paediatric ophthalmology services offered at the hospital provide treatment for all types vision-related problems in children, some of which are listed below:\n<ul>\n 	<li>Refractive error</li>\n 	<li>Amblyopia (Lazy eye)</li>\n 	<li>Paediatric cataract</li>\n 	<li>Paediatric squint</li>\n 	<li>Nystagmus</li>\n 	<li>Low vision</li>\n 	<li>Ocular trauma</li>\n</ul>\nIn addition to the above-mentioned issues, the paediatric ophthalmology department, in collaboration with the retina department, takes an active part in screening and visually rehabilitating kids suffering from Retinopathy of Prematurity (ROP).\n\nWith the glaucoma and oculoplasty department, common childhood problems such as paediatric glaucoma and oculoplasty disorders (nasolacrimal duct obstruction, ptosis, entropion, blepharophimosis, etc.) are also treated here. In addition, the strabismology services offered by this department provide treatment to adult patients suffering from double vision and squint.\n\nThis department examines and treats around 10,000 patients each year, which include the surgical treatment of around 2,500 children per year.\n\nThis department is also actively involved in school screening in the Pune and Satara districts to help in the earliest possible detection of ophthalmic conditions among children. This community outreach program helps paediatric patients to receive the best possible ophthalmic care at the earliest.','Ped. Opthalomolgy','Vision impairment in childhood has a dramatic impact not only on the social development of the child, but also on their learning capability and potential.','inherit','closed','closed','','93-autosave-v1','','','2019-06-11 12:13:28','2019-06-11 12:13:28','',93,'http://local.hvd.com/2019/05/09/93-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(173,1,'2019-05-09 06:46:20','2019-05-09 06:46:20','','Creating-ophthalmologists-future','','inherit','open','closed','','creating-ophthalmologists-future','','','2019-05-19 20:50:14','2019-05-19 20:50:14','',16,'http://local.hvd.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Creating-ophthalmologists-future.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(174,1,'2019-05-09 06:46:34','2019-05-09 06:46:34','<div class=\"home-block-wrapper clearfix\">\n<div class=\"first-block\"><span class=\"home-block-img\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/Book-an-appointment.png\"></span><span class=\"home-block-title\">Book an Appointment</span><span class=\"home-block-desc\">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elite</span></div>\n<div class=\"second-block\"><span class=\"home-block-img\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/Doctors.png\"></span><span class=\"home-block-title\">Doctors</span><span class=\"home-block-desc\">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elite</span></div>\n<div class=\"third-block\"><span class=\"home-block-img\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"wp-content/themes/hvd/assets/images/Donate.png\"></span><span class=\"home-block-title\">Donate</span><span class=\"home-block-desc\">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elite</span></div>\n</div>','Home page','','inherit','closed','closed','','16-revision-v1','','','2019-05-09 06:46:34','2019-05-09 06:46:34','',16,'http://local.hvd.com/2019/05/0