n to deal with the same.</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Salient features of the hospital:</p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Reach out program up to 350 km. from the hospital premises (Community Ophthalmology Institute)</li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The provision of free treatment to more than 60% cases</li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The provision of postgraduate and paramedical training</li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The promotion of research projects at the hospital’s in-house research centre</li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Super-specialty services in cornea, vitreo retina, medical retina, glaucoma, oculoplasty, low vision, contact lens and pediatric ophthalmology</li>\n</ul>','HVD at a Glance','','publish','closed','closed','','hvd-at-a-glance','','','2019-06-25 13:59:05','2019-06-25 13:59:05','',0,'http://local.hvd.com/?page_id=192',0,'page','',0),(193,1,'2019-05-16 06:10:09','2019-05-16 06:10:09','','About Us','','inherit','closed','closed','','192-revision-v1','','','2019-05-16 06:10:09','2019-05-16 06:10:09','',192,'http://local.hvd.com/2019/05/16/192-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(194,1,'2019-05-16 08:02:17','2019-05-16 08:02:17','a:7:{s:8:\"location\";a:1:{i:0;a:1:{i:0;a:3:{s:5:\"param\";s:13:\"page_template\";s:8:\"operator\";s:2:\"==\";s:5:\"value\";s:19:\"templates/about.php\";}}}s:8:\"position\";s:6:\"normal\";s:5:\"style\";s:7:\"default\";s:15:\"label_placement\";s:3:\"top\";s:21:\"instruction_placement\";s:5:\"label\";s:14:\"hide_on_screen\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}','About','about','publish','closed','closed','','group_5cdd0db0469e5','','','2019-05-16 11:44:24','2019-05-16 11:44:24','',0,'http://local.hvd.com/?post_type=acf-field-group&#038;p=194',0,'acf-field-group','',0),(195,1,'2019-05-16 08:02:17','2019-05-16 08:02:17','a:10:{s:4:\"type\";s:7:\"wysiwyg\";s:12:\"instructions\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"required\";i:0;s:17:\"conditional_logic\";i:0;s:7:\"wrapper\";a:3:{s:5:\"width\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"cl