 wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1>WHO IS AN OPTOMETRIST?</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://www.hvdeh.org/images/Optometry2.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>An Optometrist is a primary health care professional who is institutionally educated and clinically trained in the art and science of Optometry. Professional education in Optometry is necessary to efficiently manage any optical trade including dispensing of spectacles</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Objectives:</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>To prepare the students to assist the ophthalmologist in eye institutes, hospitals &amp; primary eye care unit.</li><li>To enable students to estimate refractive errors and dispense glasses.</li><li>To enable students to use common instruments in the (just patients units and perform simple ophthalmic supervision)</li><li>To enable students to participate in eye health promotion activities in the community.</li><li>To enable the learners to teach optometry at a school/college of optometry, enable learners to conduct research in ophthalmic field.</li><li>To enable students to produce and select appropriate optical aids including spectacles and Low Vision devices.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Scope and Career Options</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Assist ophthalmologists in hospital / clinic.</li><li>Practice in optical establishments</li><li>Run optical shop</li><li>Have excellent job opportunities overseas.</li><li>Offer clinical services to multinationals dealing, with the manufacturing and distribution of ophthalmic lenses, contact lenses and ophthalmic instruments.</li><li>Start manufacturing unit for optical lenses.</li><li>For those interested in higher studies Graduation / Post Graduation in the form of fellowships, M.Sc., M. Phil and PhD programs are available.<